name: Jellymix
description:
Showcase images were generated with VAE from Color101 VAE without edit and inpainting, this new VAE can generate more vibrant color than the other, old V1 models being generated with VAE from orangemix.

V2 update:

  1. Enhances finger and toe details.

  2. Combines styles of V1(realistic) and V1(natural).

Important Note:

Directly generate 864x1280 image, with DPM++ SDE Karras, 60 steps, clip skip 1 is recommended. Using highres fix is not recommended, use Multidiffusion with Controlnet to upscale instead.
